íŸ@a52177db6ee3f542d0e091e36a7a6bfb100f6e402c849709f8992908dee98702⁄∞Title: title: polars selector by-name
Path: Examples
Content:
Create a selector for columns by name
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> polars selector by-name foo bar


```
Add 10 to specific columns using with-column
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b c]; [1 2 3] [4 5 6]]
                    | polars into-df
                    | polars with-column ((polars selector by-name a c) + 10)
                    | polars collect
